<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Huntington Hills</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Established in the late sixties, Huntington Hills exudes a quaint charm that is fondly reminiscent of the yesteryears and reminds you of the life as it was half a century ago.</p>
            <p class="par-xl">A pet-friendly neighborhood, the community in Huntington Hills is conveniently located at the base of the Nose Hill and offers some of the most affordable housing options in the entire city. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Homes for sale in Huntington Hills include a variety of residential units ranging from duplexes, townhomes, condos and beautiful resort-like retirement homes, with an average cost of a property being in the range of $380,000. </p>
